{"tid":945082,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"將一首歌既你同我調轉","createTime":"2018-12-17T15:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T15:12:50.000Z","uid":118202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aaaaa437bc596559cd243051d683951a75237b6e","tid":945082,"uid":118202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"風光裡走過了幾千里 一轉身 卻在原地 <br />\n追憶裡一切的好東西 也溢滿 我的趣味 <br />\n如濃茶裡 滲著愛 滲著快樂滲著我 讓你可偷偷細味 <br />\n共我舉杯 微妙人生裡 終於有我 有了生機"},{"pid":"e3213b0380ecb1ebfafd06231bf9787e37ff7dec","tid":945082,"uid":118202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:05:26.000Z","msg":"你那天經過碰著我 我笑得比這世上美 <br />\n叫你不得不追求我 世界中一切亦無味 不一起 <br />\n我也許不算最完美 卻更加使你掛念我 <br />\n叫你捨不得不留起 時分秒 來共我一起 <br />\n叫你不得不接近我"},{"pid":"daa0efeba165b232792df080b35af81fd8d1cf03","tid":945082,"uid":211158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚有趣呀"},{"pid":"ac6d1c06567795b17974bb205190a075876add52","tid":945082,"uid":225620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"我有找幸福的自由<br />\n你未夠她得天獨厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}